==English==

===Pronunciation===
/An' uh gram/

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# ''In its simplest form:'' A word that is created by rearranging the letters of another word. 
# In a more complex form'': A sentence or phrase that is formed by rearranging the letters of another word or phrase.

